@startuml
!define Garrow(a,b,c) a -> b : c
node "User Browser" as User
node "Web API (Auth Filter)" as API
database "SQL Server (Encrypted)" as DB

User -> API : HTTPS Post (Student Marks)
API -> API : Validate Input / JWT Check
API -> DB : Parameterized Query (SP)
DB -> API : Success
API -> User : 201 Created
@enduml